In the Matter of 141 AVENUE A ASSOCIATES, Respondent,
v.
Jay KLEIN, Appellant. 2018-579 Court of Appeals of New York. August 30, 2018

***931Motion for leave to appeal dismissed upon the ground that this Court does not have jurisdiction to entertain a motion for leave to appeal from the order of the Appellate Division entered in this proceeding commenced in the Civil Court of the City of New York (see N.Y. Const., art. VI, § 3 [b][7]; CPLR 5602[a] ).
